1Ô∏è‚É£ Count the Number of Movies vs TV Shows.
SELECT 
    type,
    COUNT(*) AS total_count
FROM netflix
GROUP BY type;

Objective: Find how many movies and TV shows are available on Netflix.

2Ô∏è‚É£ Find the Most Common Rating for Movies and TV Shows.
SELECT 
    type,
    rating,
    COUNT(*) AS rating_count
FROM netflix
GROUP BY type, rating
ORDER BY type, rating_count DESC;

Objective: Show which ratings (like TV-MA, PG, etc.) appear most for each content type.

3Ô∏è‚É£ List All Movies Released in a Specific Year (e.g., 2020).
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE release_year = 2020;

Objective: Get all movies released in the year 2020.


4Ô∏è‚É£ Find the Top 5 Countries with the Most Content.
SELECT 
    country,
    COUNT(*) AS total_content
FROM netflix
WHERE country IS NOT NULL AND country <> ''
GROUP BY country
ORDER BY total_content DESC
LIMIT 5;

Objective: Find which 5 countries have the most Netflix content.

5Ô∏è‚É£ Identify the Longest Movie.
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE type = 'Movie'
ORDER BY CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(duration, ' ', 1) AS UNSIGNED) DESC
LIMIT 1;

Objective: Find the movie with the longest duration.

6Ô∏è‚É£ Find Content Added in the Last 5 Years.
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE STR_TO_DATE(date_added, '%M %d, %Y') >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL 5 YEAR;

Objective: Find content that was added to Netflix in the past 5 years.

7Ô∏è‚É£ Find All Movies/TV Shows by Director 'Rajiv Chilaka'.
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE director LIKE '%Rajiv Chilaka%';

Objective: List all content directed by Rajiv Chilaka.

8Ô∏è‚É£ List All TV Shows with More Than 5 Seasons**
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE type = 'TV Show'
  AND CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(duration, ' ', 1) AS UNSIGNED) > 5;

Objective: Find TV shows that have more than 5 seasons.

9Ô∏è‚É£ Count the Number of Content Items in Each Genre.
SELECT 
    listed_in AS genre,
    COUNT(*) AS total_content
FROM netflix
GROUP BY listed_in
ORDER BY total_content DESC;

Objective: Count how many titles belong to each genre category.


üîü Find Top 5 Years with the Highest Content Release in India.
SELECT 
    release_year,
    COUNT(*) AS total_release
FROM netflix
WHERE country LIKE '%India%'
GROUP BY release_year
ORDER BY total_release DESC
LIMIT 5;

Objective: Show the top 5 years when India released the most content on Netflix.

1Ô∏è‚É£1Ô∏è‚É£ List All Movies that are Documentaries.
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE listed_in LIKE '%Documentaries%';

Objective: Find all movies or shows that are documentaries.

1Ô∏è‚É£2Ô∏è‚É£ Find All Content Without a Director.
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE director IS NULL OR director = '';

Objective:** List all content that doesn‚Äôt have a director‚Äôs name.

1Ô∏è‚É£3Ô∏è‚É£ Find How Many Movies Actor 'Salman Khan' Appeared in the Last 10 Years.
SELECT *
FROM netflix
WHERE casts LIKE '%Salman Khan%'
  AND release_year >= YEAR(CURDATE()) - 10;


Objective:** Find all movies or shows featuring Salman Khan from the past 10 years.

1Ô∏è‚É£4Ô∏è‚É£ Find the Top 10 Actors in Indian Movies.
SELECT 
    casts,
    COUNT(*) AS total_appearances
FROM netflix
WHERE country LIKE '%India%'
GROUP BY casts
ORDER BY total_appearances DESC
LIMIT 10;

Objective: Find actors who appear most often in Indian content.

1Ô∏è‚É£5Ô∏è‚É£ Categorize Content Based on 'Kill' or 'Violence' Keywords.
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN description LIKE '%kill%' OR description LIKE '%violence%' THEN 'Bad'
        ELSE 'Good'
    END AS category,
    COUNT(*) AS total_content
FROM netflix
GROUP BY category;

Objective:** Classify content as ‚ÄúGood‚Äù or ‚ÄúBad‚Äù depending on keywords in the description.
